nodes.bodyText:
Can extract this Math.min... to a new method:
getMaxParallelThreads(Collection servicesToHandle) {
Math.min(servicesToDelete.size(), applicationConfiguration.getServiceHandlingMaxParallelThreads());
}
Or even add new method in ForkJoinPoolUtil that handles the collection, or refactor ParallelExecutor to not be so SLP specific

